content format
===============================================================================
(*) Meta
    > Creation Time Stamp
    > Modify Time Stamp
    > Access level
    > Type
    > Categories

(*) Content
    > Title
    > Categories
    > Content

(*) Elements
    > Link, Image, inline-HTML
    > Newline, Paragraph-Space
    > Caption

(*) To Handle
    > Headline		==
    > Linebreaks	double space
    > New paragraph	empty line
    > i	  		* *
    > b			** **
    > link		[name](url)
    > img		![name](url)

    1. Lines the text
    2. Seperate on == and empty line